column16: Chris Young grounds out to first baseman Garrett Jones.    Justin Upton scores.    Adam LaRoche to 3rd.    Mark Reynolds to 2nd.
Mark Reynolds walks.    Adam LaRoche to 2nd.
Adam LaRoche singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ryan Church.    Justin Upton to 3rd.
Justin Upton pops out to second baseman Akinori Iwamura.
Tony Abreu singles on a line drive to left fielder Lastings Milledge.
Conor Jackson grounds out, third baseman Andy LaRoche to first baseman Jeff Clement.
Augie Ojeda grounds out, shortstop Ronny Cedeno to first baseman Jeff Clement.
Jamey Carroll grounds into double play, second baseman Akinori Iwamura to shortstop Bobby Crosby to first baseman Garrett Jones.    Garret Anderson out at 2nd.
Garret Anderson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Delwyn Young.    Ronnie Belliard scores.
Ronnie Belliard triples (1) on a fly ball to right fielder Delwyn Young.    James Loney scores.
James Loney singles on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Church.    Matt Kemp scores.

Matt Kemp doubles (3) on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Church.    Rafael Furcal scores.  Reed Johnson out at home on the throw, left fielder Ryan Church to shortstop Bobby Crosby to catcher Ryan Doumit.   Matt Kemp to 3rd on the throw.
Reed Johnson singles on a ground ball to third baseman Andy LaRoche.    Rafael Furcal to 2nd.
Rafael Furcal singles on a line drive to right fielder Delwyn Young.
